Empress Dowager wants to send the nun

94
00:07:58,880 --> 00:07:59,640
to the Western State

95
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:02,700
to give the junior Prince of Nanchen a favor.

96
00:08:02,900 --> 00:08:03,460
Second,

97
00:08:03,580 --> 00:08:04,940
