115
00:08:53,020 --> 00:08:53,980
You can't dislike

116
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:55,540
her like this.

117
00:08:58,060 --> 00:08:59,380
If she is good to you,

118
00:08:59,740 --> 00:09:01,020
I won't dislike her.

119
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:02,380
Don't worry.

120
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:09,220
Your Highness,

121
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:10,380
Princess.

122
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:12,580
What's up?

123
00:09:12,820 --> 00:09:14,660
By order of Empress Dowager,

124
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:16,060
some of the Cui family directly drove a carriage from the palace gate

125
00:09:16,180 --> 00:09:17,300
to her bedding hall.

126
00:09:21,220 --> 00:09:22,700
Did you see who got off the carriage?

127
00:09:22,820 --> 00:09:23,500
Many of

128
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:24,660
the Cui clan.

129
00:09:37,140 --> 00:09:38,980
If you want to see me,

130
00:09:39,100 --> 00:09:40,860
I can go to your mansion.

131
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:43,340
Why do you come regardless of your condition?

132
00:09:43,460 --> 00:09:46,780
I'm afraid I can't wait any more.

133
00:09:52,060 --> 00:09:53,060
You come

134
00:09:53,180 --> 00:09:55,260
for the Crown Princess' engagement?

135
00:09:55,930 --> 00:09:58,660
Now that His Majesty has concubines,

136
00:09:59,110 --> 00:10:01,690
he'll have sons soon.

137
00:10:01,900 --> 00:10:04,440
You won't allow the Prince of Guangling

138
00:10:04,820 --> 00:10:06,900
to be the Crown Prince,

139
00:10:08,020 --> 00:10:09,940
right?

140
00:10:12,380 --> 00:10:13,300
Yeah.

141
00:10:13,660 --> 00:10:16,180
The Prince of Guangling will be unqualified.

142
00:10:19,900 --> 00:10:23,700
So Shiyi won't be the Crowned Princess.

143
00:10:25,620 --> 00:10:28,500
I'm sorry.

144
00:10:29,300 --> 00:10:30,460
But...

145
00:10:30,620 --> 00:10:34,540
Please cancel Shiyi's engagement.

146
00:10:54,540 --> 00:10:55,780
My son Feng.

147
00:11:00,580 --> 00:11:03,540
I want to ask for an engagement

148
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:06,500
for him.

149
00:11:09,340 --> 00:11:11,620
Which girl do you think suits him?

150
00:11:11,740 --> 00:11:12,900
Tell me.

151
00:11:13,460 --> 00:11:15,980
Princess of Xinghua.

152
00:11:19,560 --> 00:11:22,740
My son has been guiding Shouyang for many years.

153
00:11:23,150 --> 00:11:24,740
With many battle achievements,

154
00:11:26,580 --> 00:11:28,940
he is worthy of Her Highness.

155
00:11:33,300 --> 00:11:34,460
In the palace,

156
00:11:34,740 --> 00:11:36,220
only she

157
00:11:36,340 --> 00:11:38,540
reaches marriageable age.

158
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:40,140
But...

159
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:42,980
If she marries my son,

160
00:11:43,340 --> 00:11:46,110
the Cui clan and your family

161
00:11:46,130 --> 00:11:47,800
will be united through marriage,

162
00:11:47,980 --> 00:11:50,540
which will be good

163
00:11:51,020 --> 00:11:52,820
for you only.

164
00:11:57,620 --> 00:11:59,020
Empress Dowager.

165
00:12:09,100 --> 00:12:09,980
OK.

166
00:12:10,900 --> 00:12:13,260
I'll certainly agree with this marriage

167
00:12:14,300 --> 00:12:15,580
to make up for what the royal family

168
00:12:15,700 --> 00:12:17,820
owe your family.

169
00:12:18,020 --> 00:12:20,060
Thank you, Empress Dowager.

170
00:12:28,860 --> 00:12:38,220
[Jiafu Palace]

171
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:35,220
Shiyi.

172
00:12:37,700 --> 00:12:38,580
Shiyi.

173
00:12:39,980 --> 00:12:41,020
Your Highness, please behave yourself.

174
00:12:44,300 --> 00:12:46,180
I won't definitely cancel our engagement.

175
00:12:51,180 --> 00:12:52,260
Your Highness,

176
00:12:52,420 --> 00:12:53,500
as a favored prince,

177
00:12:53,820 --> 00:12:55,140
