179
00:12:56,500 --> 00:12:57,820
Now that Empress Dowager has cancelled our engagement,

180
00:12:57,940 --> 00:12:58,620
don't give your heart

181
00:12:58,740 --> 00:12:59,980
to me.

182
00:13:00,100 --> 00:13:00,940
Shut up.

183
00:13:04,220 --> 00:13:05,700
You called her in public like this.

184
00:13:05,900 --> 00:13:07,660
