191
00:13:18,980 --> 00:13:20,620
Your Highness has loved Miss Cui since childhood.

192
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:21,340
He doesn't want to

193
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:22,940
and won't hurt her.

194
00:13:27,260 --> 00:13:28,540
I'm sorry.

195
00:13:29,420 --> 00:13:30,660
Uncle, please forgive me.

196
00:13:49,820 --> 00:13:51,020
Go out of the palace

197
00:13:51,220 --> 00:13:52,260
to stay in the Residence of Cui

198
00:13:52,580 --> 00:13:54,100
