199
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:55,380
And spend some days

200
00:13:56,510 --> 00:13:57,540
with your uncle.

201
00:13:58,660 --> 00:13:59,220
Yes.

202
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:10,260
Aunt, I don't want to marry him.

