00:14:18,380 --> 00:14:20,220
The marriage between the Cui family and us

206
00:14:20,340 --> 00:14:21,940
is imperative.

207
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:24,620
Now we just let it be.

208
00:14:25,180 --> 00:14:26,540
So you must marry him.

209
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:29,380
But, but I don't like him.

210
00:14:30,100 --> 00:14:31,660
Who do you like?

211
00:14:32,020 --> 00:14:32,620
I...

