236
00:16:11,260 --> 00:16:12,860
to ask for this engagement for you.

237
00:16:12,980 --> 00:16:14,220
Do you really want your dad

238
00:16:14,340 --> 00:16:15,980
to die in anger?

239
00:16:21,540 --> 00:16:22,340
Dad,

240
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:24,220
I always

241
00:16:24,460 --> 00:16:26,140
listen to you

242
00:16:26,540 --> 00:16:28,180
and have never gone against you.

243
00:16:28,380 --> 00:16:29,500
This time,

244
00:16:31,340 --> 00:16:34,420
I beg you to cancel this engagement.

245
00:16:36,940 --> 00:16:38,660
I would rather remain single all my life

246
00:16:39,340 --> 00:16:40,660
than marry the princess.

247
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:42,860
Beat him.

248
00:16:42,980 --> 00:16:45,940
